<p>The Simple project makes a free easy-to-use BP Passport app for patients to track their own BPs, blood sugars, and medications.</p>

<h3>Free for everyone</h3>
<p>The BP Passport app is totally free and will be free forever.</p>

<h3>Very simple</h3>
<p>The BP Passport app is designed to be simple. It is easy to learn and easy to use, even for people who don't have much experience using smartphone applications.</p>

